OL,7,FAround 300 workers at a "colossally
OL,8,Fprofitable" wind turbine manufacturing
OL,9,Fgiant are being balloted for strike
OL,10,Faction over pay.
OL,12,FUnite the Union says the workers at
OL,13,FSiemens Gamesa in Hull, who build 108-
OL,14,Fmetre long wind turbine blades by
OL,15,Fhand, are angry at a four-and-a-half
OL,16,Fpercent pay offer and an "opaque"
OL,17,Fincentive scheme.
