OL,7,FThe union says that since 2018, wages
OL,8,Fat the factory on the banks of the
OL,9,FHumber estuary have dropped by almost
OL,10,F12 percent in real terms, due to below-
OL,11,FRPI inflation pay rises and the
OL,12,F"suppression of wages" through a
OL,13,Fperformance-related bonus scheme.
OL,15,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,16,Fsaid: "Siemens is a colossally
OL,17,Fprofitable company, yet wages at its
OL,18,FHull factory have fallen in real terms
OL,19,Fyear on year.
