OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FUnite says that Siemens Gamesa
OL,8,FRenewable Energy (SGRE), which owns
OL,9,Fthe factory, made #394million in
OL,10,Fprofits over the last five years and
OL,11,Fpaid out two dividends worth #226
OL,12,Fmillion during the same period. It
OL,13,Fsays SGRE's revenue is expected to
OL,14,Fdouble in 2024 to #1.5billion, with
OL,15,Fpre-tax profits on course to hit
OL,16,F#100million for the year.
OL,18,FThe workers are being balloted for
OL,19,Fstrike action until 24 July, with
OL,20,Fstrikes set to be scheduled shortly
OL,21,Fafter if members vote for it.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
