OL,7,FUnite regional co-ordinating officer
OL,8,FHarriet Eisner said: "Siemens Gamesa
OL,9,Fis set to cause huge disruption to its
OL,10,Fclients, which are constructing vital
OL,11,Foffshore windfarms, due to its own
OL,12,Fgreed.
OL,14,F"There is still time to avoid
OL,15,Findustrial action, but that requires
OL,16,Fan offer from the company that is
OL,17,Facceptable to our members."
